Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.80,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você se sente sozinho?
