Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.67,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Se eu soubesse que os olhos podem se abrir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.46,OPL2,dontextend dontearly,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,0)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Deixe a luz entrar
